|2010= 43946
|footnote = <ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.census.gov/population/www/censusdata/cencounts/files/nv190090.txt |title=census.gov, censusdata: cencounts |accessdate=2013-01-16 |archive-date=2012-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120217220423/http://www.census.gov/population/www/censusdata/cencounts/files/nv190090.txt |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://factfinder2.census.gov/ |title=factfinder2 census |accessdate=2020-10-06 |archive-date=2013-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130911234518/http://factfinder2.census.gov/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://mapserver.lib.virginia.edu/ |title=mapserver census data |accessdate=2013-01-16 |archive-date=2012-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120811110448/http://mapserver.lib.virginia.edu/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>}}

根據[[2000年美國人口普查|2000年人口普查]]，奈縣擁有32,485居民、13,309住戶和9,063家庭。<ref>{{en}}[http://www.census.gov/population/www/pop-profile/profile2000.html Population Profile of the United States: 2000] {{Wayback|url=http://www.census.gov/population/www/pop-profile/profile2000.html |date=20040113065424 }}</ref>。其[[人口密度|人口密度]]為每平方英里2居民（每平方公里1居民）。奈縣擁有15,934間房屋单位，其密度為每平方英里1間（每平方公里0.87間）。奈縣的人口是由89.63%[[歐裔美國人|白人]]、1.18%[[非裔美國人|黑人]]、1.96%[[美國土著|土著]]、0.78%[[亞裔美國人|亞洲人]]、0.32%[[太平洋岛民|太平洋岛民]]、2.98%其他[[種族|種族]]和3.15%[[混血|混血]][[种族构成|构成]]。而[[西班牙裔美国人|西班牙裔]]或[[拉丁美洲人|拉丁美洲人]]佔了人口8.35%。<ref>{{en}}[http://www.census.gov/main/www/cen2000.html Census 2000 gateway] {{Wayback|url=http://www.census.gov/main/www/cen2000.html |date=20190331194847 }}</ref>

在13,309住户中，有26.40%擁有一個或以上的兒童（18歲以下）、56.30%為夫妻、7.40%為單親家庭、而有31.90%為非家庭。其中25.70%住户為獨居，10.30%為同居長者。平均每戶有2.42人，而平均每個家庭則有2.90人。在32,485居民中，有23.70%為18歲以下、5.40%為18至24歲、24.00%為25至44歲、28.50%為45至64歲以及18.40%為65歲以上。人口的年齡中位數為43歲，每100個女性就有105.10個男性。每100個成年女性（18歲以上）就有104.70個成年男性。<ref name="Census">{{cite web |url=http://2010.census.gov/2010census/data/apportionment-pop-text.php |title=Resident Population Data: Population Change |date=2010-12-23 |publisher=[[United_States_Census_Bureau|United States Census Bureau]] |accessdate=2010-12-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101225031104/http://2010.census.gov/2010census/data/apportionment-pop-text.php |archivedate=2010-12-25 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

奈縣的住戶收入中位數為$36,024，而家庭收入中位數則為$41,642。男性的收入中位數為$37,276，而女性的收入中位數則為$22,394。奈縣的[[人均收入|人均收入]]為$17,962。約7.30%家庭和10.70%人口在[[貧窮線|貧窮線]]以下。<ref name="Census"/>

與美國西部許多鄉村縣份相同，奈縣的自殺率相對高<ref>[http://www.reviewjournal.com/cgi-bin/printable.cgi?/lvrj_home/2000/Oct-16-Mon-2000/news/14605459.html RURAL SUICIDE: Soaring rates puzzling] {{Wayback|url=http://www.reviewjournal.com/cgi-bin/printable.cgi?%2Flvrj_home%2F2000%2FOct-16-Mon-2000%2Fnews%2F14605459.html |date=20090713230022 }} Las Vegas Review-Journal: ''Rural Suicide: Soaring rates puzzling''</ref>。根據疾病預防控制中心統計<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://webappa.cdc.gov/cdc_mxt3/dataView.asp?POI_SELECT=1989-1998&COUNTY_CAUSE_SELECT=SUI00_ADJ_EB&COLOR_SELECT=Default%20Colors%20%283%20colors%29&sourcePage=%2Fcdc_mxt3%2FNationByCounty.asp&mapState=773.919143558772%2C-117.021701340677%2C38.5020874233089%2CFalse%2CFalse%2CFalse%2CFalse%2CFalse%2CFalse%2CTrue%2CTrue%2CTrue%2CFalse&STATES_SELECT=NV |title=CDC Statistics: Nye county |access-date=2022-02-22 |archive-date=2020-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201123039/https://webappa.cdc.gov/cdc_mxt3/dataView.asp?POI_SELECT=1989-1998&COUNTY_CAUSE_SELECT=SUI00_ADJ_EB&COLOR_SELECT=Default%20Colors%20%283%20colors%29&sourcePage=%2Fcdc_mxt3%2FNationByCounty.asp&mapState=773.919143558772%2C-117.021701340677%2C38.5020874233089%2CFalse%2CFalse%2CFalse%2CFalse%2CFalse%2CFalse%2CTrue%2CTrue%2CTrue%2CFalse&STATES_SELECT=NV |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，奈縣每年的自殺率為每100,000個人有28.7561個人自殺。奈縣的自殺率在內華達州中排第三。比奈縣高的縣份為[[白松縣_(內華達州)|白松縣]]（34.3058）和[[萊昂縣_(內華達州)|萊昂縣]]（30.8917）。奈縣的自殺率比整個州的自殺率（22.96）高，且內華達州的自殺率已是美國之冠。可見其自殺率相當之高。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://webappa.cdc.gov/cdc_mxt3/dataView.asp?POI_SELECT=1989-1998&STATE_CAUSE_SELECT=SUIC9698_AGEADJ&COLOR_SELECT=Default%20Colors%20%283%20colors%29&sourcePage=%2Fcdc_mxt3%2FNationByState.asp&mapState=3420%2C-95.8865999887645%2C34.4056999586157%2CFalse%2CFalse%2CFalse%2CFalse%2CFalse%2CFalse%2CTrue%2CFalse%2CTrue%2CFalse |title=CDC Statistics: Nevada |access-date=2022-02-22 |archive-date=2020-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201112804/https://webappa.cdc.gov/cdc_mxt3/dataView.asp?POI_SELECT=1989-1998&STATE_CAUSE_SELECT=SUIC9698_AGEADJ&COLOR_SELECT=Default%20Colors%20%283%20colors%29&sourcePage=%2Fcdc_mxt3%2FNationByState.asp&mapState=3420%2C-95.8865999887645%2C34.4056999586157%2CFalse%2CFalse%2CFalse%2CFalse%2CFalse%2CFalse%2CTrue%2CFalse%2CTrue%2CFalse |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

